  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<p><br />We are looking for a motivated and dynamic <strong>Business Development Executive</strong> to support our growth and expand our client base. If you enjoy building relationships, identifying opportunities, and working in a fast-paced, service-oriented environment, we’d love to hear from you.</p><h3>🔍 Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Identify and develop new business opportunities</li><li>Generate leads and follow up on client inquiries</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients</li><li>Prepare quotations, proposals, and service presentations</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth service delivery</li><li>Monitor market trends and provide business insights</li><li>Support marketing and business development initiatives</li><li>Able to travel overseas when required for client meetings, business development activities, and company assignments</li></ul></p><h3>🎯 Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Business, Marketing, Management, or related fields</p></li><li><p>1–3 years of experience in business development, sales, or client-facing roles</p><p><br /><em>(Fresh graduates with strong interest are welcome to apply)</em></p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, proactive, and results-driven</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office</p></li></ul>",
